name: Jackie Swart
description: I’m happy,content,have a positive attitude about almost everything.Am thoughtful,polite,giving,listener, Knight in shining Armor,give back and friendly.Am equally comfortable going out for a nice dinner and wine.l am more likely to go to a quiet coffee shop than a noisy crowded bar.I prefer a woman with open mind and I don’t smoke or use drugs of any kind,l want same in a partner.Also,I enjoy traveling,learning new things,watching movies,walking,listening to music.
